WorldStage Newsonline– Capital Hotels Plc has announced that the name of its Hotel located at Abuja has been changed from “Sheraton Abuja Hotel” to “Abuja Continental Hotel”. In a notice at the Nigerian Exchange signed by Alex Ugwuanyi, the company said the “hotel has also been reopened for operations while renovations are ongoing to bring the Hotel to the standard befitting its status as a Five Star Hotel.”